		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<iframe frameborder="0" scrolling="no" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0"
					src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Sydney%2C%20Australia&#038;t=m&#038;z=10&#038;output=embed&#038;iwloc=near"
					title="Sydney, Australia"
					aria-label="Sydney, Australia"
			></iframe>
			<figure><img width="512" height="512" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/location-3.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure><h2>Address</h2><p>Sydney, Australia</p>		
			<figure><img width="512" height="512" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/time.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure><h2>Phone</h2><p>+111 22-33-444<br>Mon - Sat: 8am - 10pm; Sun CLOSED</p>		
			<figure><img width="512" height="512" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/send.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure><h2>Contact</h2><p>contact@youroceanwpsite.com</p>		
			<form id="wpforms-form-664" data-formid="664" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/wp-admin/admin-ajax.php" data-token="bc0d159555c27c0ffb98881c6a2219c6"><noscript>Please enable JavaScript in your browser to complete this form.</noscript><label for="wpforms-664-field_0">First Name *</label><input type="text" id="wpforms-664-field_0" name="wpforms[fields][0]" placeholder="First Name" required><label for="wpforms-664-field_3">Last Name *</label><input type="text" id="wpforms-664-field_3" name="wpforms[fields][3]" placeholder="Last Name" required><label for="wpforms-664-field_1">Your Email *</label><input type="email" id="wpforms-664-field_1" name="wpforms[fields][1]" placeholder="Your Email" required><label for="wpforms-664-field_4">Your Phone</label><input type="text" id="wpforms-664-field_4" name="wpforms[fields][4]" placeholder="Your Phone" ><label for="wpforms-664-field_5">Your Subject</label><input type="text" id="wpforms-664-field_5" name="wpforms[fields][5]" placeholder="Your Subject" ><label for="wpforms-664-field_2">Your Message *</label><textarea id="wpforms-664-field_2" name="wpforms[fields][2]" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea><label for="wpforms-664-field-hp">Phone</label><input type="text" name="wpforms[hp]" id="wpforms-664-field-hp"><input type="hidden" name="wpforms[id]" value="664">			<input
				type="hidden"
				name="wpforms[nonce]"
				value="f7438632e0"
			/>
			<input type="hidden" name="wpforms[author]" value="6"><button type="submit" name="wpforms[submit]" id="wpforms-submit-664" data-alt-text="Sending..." data-submit-text="Submit Message" aria-live="assertive" value="wpforms-submit">Submit Message</button></form>  <!-- .wpforms-container -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Privacy Policy]]></title>
		<link>http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/?page_id=3</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 24 Jun 2025 13:01:17 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[CYRUS]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/?page_id=3</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Who we are</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Our website address is: http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Comments</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Media</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Cookies</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Embedded content from other websites</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Who we share your data with</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">How long we retain your data</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What rights you have over your data</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Where your data is sent</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->
<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->
]]></content:encoded>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="768" height="194" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arch-768x194.png" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arch-768x194.png 768w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arch-300x76.png 300w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/arch.png 869w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" />															
					<h1>HEALTHCARE EXCELLENCE</h1>				
					<h2>consolata hospital mathari</h2>				
					<h2><b>for compassionate healthcare services you can believe in</b></h2>				
					<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/outpatient-services/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
									Explore
					</a>
					<h2><a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/about-page/">READ MORE</a></h2>				
															<img width="1024" height="184" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/85-years-banner-1024x184.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/85-years-banner-1024x184.jpg 1024w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/85-years-banner-300x54.jpg 300w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/85-years-banner-768x138.jpg 768w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/85-years-banner.jpg 1349w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
															<img width="1024" height="184" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mathari-SHA-Services-web-1024x184-2.png" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mathari-SHA-Services-web-1024x184-2.png 1024w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mathari-SHA-Services-web-1024x184-2-300x54.png 300w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Mathari-SHA-Services-web-1024x184-2-768x138.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															
					<h2>About us</h2>				
					<h2>our purpose</h2>				
					<h2>Consolata Hospital Mathari is a private, faith-based level 5 healthcare institution in the bustling Mathari neighbourhood of Nyeri County, Kenya. The hospital was established in 1938 by the Consolata Missionaries to provide quality healthcare services to the local community and beyond.
With a team of highly trained and experienced medical professionals, Consolata Hospital Mathari is renowned for its exceptional healthcare services. These services are offered in a compassionate and patient-centred environment. The hospital has a bed capacity of 200 with various medical services, including general surgery, paediatrics, obstetrics and gynaecology, internal medicine, orthopaedics, and dermatology among others.</h2>				
					<h2>Since our founding, our purpose has been to provide high-quality, affordable, and accessible healthcare services to the local community and beyond, delivered in a compassionate and patient-centred environment.
The hospital is committed to improving its patients’ health and well-being by offering a wide range of medical services. We promote disease prevention and health education programs and invest in modern medical equipment and technology. Indeed, we are dedicated to upholding our core values of responsiveness, professionalism, compassion, teamwork, integrity, and dignity in all interactions with patients, their families, and the wider community.</h2>				
					<h2>Caring For You, Your Family &amp; The Community</h2>				
					<h2>Our Medical Services</h2>				
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/maternal-child-health-and-maternity/">
							<img width="735" height="458" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Consolata-Hospital-Mathari-Website-CSR-Activity-INDIVIDUAL-PAGE-MAIN-IMAGE-3.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Consolata-Hospital-Mathari-Website-CSR-Activity-INDIVIDUAL-PAGE-MAIN-IMAGE-3.jpg 735w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Consolata-Hospital-Mathari-Website-CSR-Activity-INDIVIDUAL-PAGE-MAIN-IMAGE-3-300x187.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 735px) 100vw, 735px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/major-surgery/">
							<img width="547" height="340" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/surgery.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/surgery.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/surgery-300x186.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/dialysis">
							<img width="547" height="330" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dialysis.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dialysis.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/dialysis-300x181.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
					<h2><b>MATERNAL, CHILD HEALTH &amp; MATERNITY SERVICES</b><br><br>We provide comprehensive maternal, child health, and maternity services to support mothers and children throughout the pregnancy journey.</h2>				
					<h2><b>SURGERY</b><br><br>With our advanced operating theatre equipped with modern surgical equipment, and staffed by qualified personnel, we offer surgical services to patients.</h2>				
					<h2><b>DIALYSIS</b><br><br>We have an 8-bed dialysis unit open 24/7 and supported by nephrology nurses, a full-time medical doctor, and a visiting consultant nephrologist.</h2>				
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/laboratory-services">
							<img width="547" height="340" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/lab-services.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/lab-services.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/lab-services-300x186.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/radiology-and-imaging">
							<img width="547" height="340" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/radiology.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/radiology.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/radiology-300x186.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/outpatient-services/">
							<img width="547" height="330" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/outpatient-services.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/outpatient-services.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/outpatient-services-300x181.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
					<h2><b>LABORATORY</b> <b>SERVICES</b><br><br>With our well-equipped laboratory, we perform all major medical diagnostic tests such as blood, urine, and stool among others.</h2>				
					<h2><b>RADIOLOGY &amp; IMAGING</b><br><br>The hospital provides radiology services for diagnostic and therapeutic purposes. We have modern radiology equipment such as X-rays, ultrasound, and CT scan machines.</h2>				
					<h2><b>OUTPATIENT SERVICES</b><br><br>We offer a number of outpatient services designed to cater to the medical needs of patients who do not require hospitalization or have been discharged from the hospital.</h2>				
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/counselling-services">
							<img width="547" height="340" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/couselling.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/couselling.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/couselling-300x186.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/ear-nose-throat-unit">
							<img width="547" height="340" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ear-unit.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ear-unit.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/ear-unit-300x186.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
																<a href="https://www.cmatharihospital.co.ke/ConsolataNew/critical-care-services/">
							<img width="547" height="330" src="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/care-unit.jpg" alt="" srcset="http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/care-unit.jpg 547w, http://CONSOLATA-HOSPITAL-MATHARI/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/care-unit-300x181.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px" />								</a>
					<h2><b>COUSELLING</b><br><br>The hospital provides comprehensive counselling services to help patients deal with a wide range of mental health issues, including depression, anxiety, and stress</h2>				
					<h2><b>EAR, NOSE &amp; THROAT UNIT</b><br><br>Using modern techniques like nasal endoscopy, we diagnose and treat disorders affecting the ears, nose, and throat</h2>				
					<h2>I<b>NTENSIVE CARE UNIT</b><br><br>Consolata Hospital, Mathari has a 5-bed critical care unit and is one of the cost-effective ICUs in the Mt. Kenya region</h2>				
					<h2>healthcare excellence</h2>				
					<h2>our core values</h2>				
					<h2>1. Professionalism: We demonstrate competence in what we do.
<br>2. Integrity: We are honest and demonstrate strong moral principles.
<br>3. Teamwork: We work collaboratively for a common purpose.
<br>4. Responsiveness: We answer readily to your needs and suggestions.
<br>5. Compassion and care: We desire to help alleviate your suffering and pay attention to your needs and concerns with compassion, joy, peace, kindness, mercy, and hope all in our care.
<br>6. Dignity: We exercise the spirit of humanity, honor, respecting the worth of each person that we meet and encounter in keen observation that our patients, visitors, co-workers deserve our respect</h2>
